<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM6.5.5">
<l>viṭaiyēḻ veṉṟu meṉtō ḷāyccik kaṉpaṉāy</l>
<l>naṭaiyāl niṉṟa marutam cāytta nātaṉūr</l>
<l>peṭaiyō ṭaṉṉam peyvaḷai yārtam piṉceṉṟu</l>
<l>naṭaiyō ṭiyali nāṇi yoḷikkum naṟaiyūrē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The city of the lord who pushed [over] the sturdy marutam by [simply] walking</l>
<l>And who, conquering seven bulls, became the beloved</l>
<l rend="indent">of the soft-shouldered herdess,</l>
<l>Is Naṟaiyūr where a swan and his mate, following behind</l>
<l rend="indent">those with tight bangles,</l>
<l>Competing with [their] gait, hide, being embarrassed.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
